title: Windows 7 SP1 AIO 36in1 sv-SE Sept 2013

Win7.AIO.36in1.sv-SE.Sept2013

[ RELEASE INFO ]

  Hotfixes 2013-09-10 included

  File:		Win7.AIO.36in1.sv-SE.Sept2013.iso
  Source:	32bit: X17-59271 
		64bit: X17-59273 
		
  Size: 	5,25GB
  Format: 	Bootable ISO (DVD-DL 8,5GB or USB)
   
  CRC32: 	21472e09
  MD5:		6e38c69a77e4f8c86c39a721049ff676
  SHA-1: 	190728141bf902016eda555d82f9c772e614f5de
   
[ CONTENTS ]

  Setupcomplete / Post-install:
  * KB890930
  * Defender updates 
  * .NET Framework 4.5.1 RC (only on marked editions)
  * Internet Explorer 10 

  Limited to Pre-Activated:
  * Windows Loader 2.2.1 by Daz

[ EDITIONS INCLUDED ]

  32-bit

  * Windows 7 Home Basic     | Activated | .NET 4.5.1 | Activated with .NET 4.5.1
  * Windows 7 Home Premium   | Activated | .NET 4.5.1 | Activated with .NET 4.5.1
  * Windows 7 Professional   | Activated | .NET 4.5.1 | Activated with .NET 4.5.1
  * Windows 7 Ultimate       | Activated | .NET 4.5.1 | Activated with .NET 4.5.1
  
  64-bit

[ COMMENTS ]
 
  Setup information:
  * There are 4 different types of installation to choose from for each edition;

    1. Standard install
    2. Standard install with Activation
    3. Standard install with .NET 4.5.1 
    4. Standard install with .NET 4.5.1 and Activation
  
  * Indexes shown with Pre-Activated in the description field will be activated.
